text: Sukinda Road railway station is a railway station on the East Coast Railway network in the state of Odisha, India. It serves Sukinda Road. Its code is SKND. It has one platforms. Passenger, Express trains halt at Sukinda Road railway station. ==Major Trains== * Puri - Barbil Express * Visakhapatnam - Tatanagar Weekly Superfast Express ==See also== * Jajpur district ==References== Category:Railway stations in Jajpur district Category:Khurda Road railway division
title: Sukinda Road railway station
